#~ "If the mouse supports resolution switching, the <guilabel>Sensor "
#~ "Resolution</guilabel> radio button group will be enabled, and you can "
#~ "switch from <guilabel>400 counts per inch</guilabel> to <guilabel>800 "
#~ "counts per inch</guilabel> and back. If you use <guilabel>800 counts per "
